# CODEOWNERS - Claude Agent Ownership Mapping
# 
# This file maps code paths to responsible Claude agents.
# When files matching these patterns are changed, the corresponding
# agent will be automatically invoked for review.
#
# Format: pattern @claude-agent-name
# Agents are defined in .claude/subagents/

# Default reviewer for all files
* @claude-reviewer

